♫ I would put a smile through your tears ♫

772
01:09:09,490 --> 01:09:15,110
♫ Let me kiss goodbye on your cheeks ♫

773
01:09:15,110 --> 01:09:21,480
♫ And go on and on and on ♫

774
01:09:47,740 --> 01:09:51,090
♫ Memories wear protective coloration ♫

775
01:09:51,090 --> 01:09:54,140
♫ Ambushing in the middle of the night ♫

776
01:09:54,140 --> 01:09:59,740
♫ A quiet strike ♫

777
01:09:59,740 --> 01:10:02,860
♫ Streetlights awaiting dusk ♫

778
01:10:02,860 --> 01:10:05,150
♫ Still awaiting as always ♫

779
01:10:05,150 --> 01:10:08,340
♫ Nothing is impossible ♫

780
01:10:08,340 --> 01:10:12,690
♫ Even if no one is perfect ♫

781
01:10:12,690 --> 01:10:17,300
♫ Holding you next to my heartbeat ♫

782
01:10:17,300 --> 01:10:20,480
♫ Tightly held the palm of my hand ♫

783
01:10:20,480 --> 01:10:25,450
♫ It remains the only farewell ♫

784
01:10:25,450 --> 01:10:30,200
♫ If I could see you again ♫

785
01:10:30,200 --> 01:10:36,870
♫ Carefully planning my gamble with you ♫

786
01:10:36,870 --> 01:10:40,940
♫ In the end I lost to you ♫

787
01:10:40,940 --> 01:10:50,240
♫ I think of you until I can no longer breathe ♫

788
01:10:50,240 --> 01:10:53,930
♫ If you were a painter ♫

789
01:10:53,930 --> 01:10:55,940
♫ Then I'll be your canvas ♫

790
01:10:55,940 --> 01:11:00,240
♫ No regrets ♫

791
01:11:00,240 --> 01:11:06,940
♫ I lost all my love to you ♫
